cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.DB, cs.DS, cs.IR 

The paper deals with the analysis of social networks, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses distributed computing systems and graph processing, which are related to systems and databases (cs.SD, cs.DB). The use of minhash signatures and Locality Sensitive Hashing for compressing and querying graph structures is related to data structures (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
